{"tid":1131324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雖遠必豬 小熊維尼故鄉！ 英國亞士頓森林晚間失火","createTime":"2019-04-29T14:52:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T19:16:03.000Z","uid":32511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7f964fb53ec0babf66dc900c24c2ed9b6f9b6944","tid":1131324,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T14:52:56.000Z","msg":"卡通小熊維尼故鄉的原型、位於英國東薩塞克斯郡（East<br />\nSussex）的亞士頓森林（Ashdown Forest），週日（28日）晚間發生火災，大火在一夜之間燒毀6英畝土地。<br />\n <br />\n綜合外媒報導，消防單位在當地時間週日晚間9時30分（台灣時間週一凌晨4時30分）獲報這座保育森林發生大火，派出6輛消防車等打火設備赴現場解決大火，現已縮減到4輛消防車在現場控制火勢。<br />\n <br />\n當地消防部門的高斯登（Andrew Gausden）表示，「在夜間發生這樣大小的火災很不尋常」，他說，盡管最近有下雨，但森林中的灌木叢非常乾燥，火勢延燒迅速。目前起火原因不明，尚未排除人為縱火。<br />\n <br />\n英國作家米爾恩（Alan Alexander Milne）曾住在亞士頓森林附近，他在1920年創造的小熊維尼故事，其故事場景「百畝森林」─小熊維尼和他朋友的家，原型就是亞士頓森林。"},{"pid":"37a1ef1b83cd6ca9af603108e6c1ca60ae4ce436","tid":1131324,"uid":2950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T14:57:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9acdaf81c8aed851c5bcd0be98e5671852b7609c","tid":1131324,"uid":117276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T14:58:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da51f2fa14d8fc940c480dee4adbd4d40a40de94","tid":1131324,"uid":136900,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T15:01:53.000Z","msg":"以為習近平故鄉喺英國森林<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15fa866fa22791b75eae2e19f7dc2eb55de8734e","tid":1131324,"uid":204306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T15:04:40.000Z","msg":"唔係陜西定河南咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99c9a7796aa455abf4b6fd744eeb39fe43651e36","tid":1131324,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T15:06:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df7cf45e6d9416749fd06e39521089fa3e09ad35","tid":1131324,"uid":156363,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T15:22:56.000Z","msg":"一定係雜種派人放火"},{"pid":"6f518faf0eb49d49dacb826be26f8577295eabaf","tid":1131324,"uid":210121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T19:16:03.000Z","msg":"小熊維尼凶多吉少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}